sentences: Kang Hee-gun (Korean: 강희건; born February 24, 1978), better known by his stage name Gary (Korean: 개리, often spelled as Garie), is a South Korean rapper, songwriter, record producer, entrepreneur, and television personality.
Since their formation in 2002, the group has produced a total of eight albums and had several hits under their belt.
In 2014, Gary made his debut as a solo artist with the mini-album Mr. Gae.
Gary was born on February 24, 1978.
